@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = ((wp.exp(tmp + 0.32) / wp.exp(v0 + 0.43)) + ((tmp + 0.58 - v0 + 0.78) / (v1 + 0.93 - v1 + 0.86)))
    v1 = (wp.abs((v1 + 0.25 * v2 + 0.98)) + (wp.cos(v2 + 0.24) + (v0 + 0.36 + v1 + 0.34)))
    tmp = tmp
    data[tid] = v0
